"""Test that we can demote a region"""
a = Region(maxdepth=8)
a.add_circles(0, np.radians(-90), np.radians(1))
_ = a.pixeldict.copy()
fpd = a.get_demoted()
if not fpd == a.pixeldict[8]:
    raise AssertionError()
for i in range(1, 8):
    if not len(a.pixeldict[i]) == 0:
        raise AssertionError()
